intent.user_query: Find the most common issue description in service tickets.

phases.goal: Execute SQL query on fitness_db: SELECT IssueDescription, COUNT(*) AS Occurrence FROM fitness_db.ServiceTickets GROUP BY IssueDescription ORDER BY Occurrence DESC QUALIFY ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY Occurrence DESC) <= 1;

arguments.sql: SELECT IssueDescription, COUNT(*) AS Occurrence FROM fitness_db.ServiceTickets GROUP BY IssueDescription ORDER BY Occurrence DESC QUALIFY ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY Occurrence DESC) <= 1;

phases.goal: Generate the final report based on the query results.
